486
00:32:33,190 --> 00:32:34,390
Permaisuri Yu akan mengadakan jamuan makan.

487
00:32:34,670 --> 00:32:35,990
Kita bisa pergi memeriksa istana.

488
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:37,340
