597
00:37:44,540 --> 00:37:45,380
Energi rohani.

598
00:37:45,660 --> 00:37:46,500
Ada semangat di sini.

599
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,540
Menurutku, itu menuju ke arah sini.

600
00:37:53,750 --> 00:37:54,620
Leluhur Agung,

601
00:37:55,350 --> 00:37:56,540
