603
00:38:01,140 --> 00:38:02,060
Kamu pergi dulu.

604
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:02,950
Saya akan melihat sekeliling.

605
00:38:14,580 --> 00:38:15,500
Yang Mulia,

606
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,340
